ockquote>好多人以為識影相係張張相影出嚟都靚  <br />\n但其實攝影師同你老母一樣都係影埋一堆meh嘅相 <br />\n只不過你老母張張都拎出嚟問人係咪好靚<br />\n<br />\n影相最難學嗰樣嘢其實係<br />\n忍心影咗幾千張但剩係拎靚嘅一張出嚟，<br />\n甚至一張都唔拎，全部都唔滿意就全部都唔要再出去影過</blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人以為一影就影到靚真係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但隨手一影都好過我呢啲影野就將舊野擺係中間放到最大嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇唔到無post出嚟嗰幾千張啫<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/020007_44ca6bfec7cf6016b48fc397c9bbe908.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F020007_44ca6bfec7cf6016b48fc397c9bbe908.jpg&h=ba5ff124&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意，你見隔離post都係一人五張相<br />\n唔會將影過嘅全部貼出黎<br />\n<br />\nBtw我覺得電話影個張條女合埋隻腳望落去舒服啲<br />\n而家望落去有啲怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cb269aa2f8effd80595c027c09ddaf001ce7c1","tid":423200,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ON9問題<br />\n<br />\n新手用a mode定m mode好<br />\n<br />\n我用開m mode<br />\n<br />\n右下角有把間尺咁既野<br />\n<br />\n負唔知幾多去正唔知幾多，咩東東黎</blockquote><br />\n呢d基本相機操作自己睇教學，睇完都唔明轉去auto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無keyword唔知點search<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過算應該ok既</blockquote><br />\n你部機執定偷架，冇說明書？"},{"pid":"22560d7070fcb9bbe3c11550ba8309c4a3d55d0d","tid":423200,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T06:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ON9問題<br />\n<br />\n新手用a mode定m mode好<br />\n<br />\n我用開m mode<br />\n<br />\n右下角有把間尺咁既野<br />\n<br />\n負唔知幾多去正唔知幾多，咩東東黎</blockquote><br />\n呢d基本相機操作自己睇教學，睇完都唔明轉去auto<img 